What is relative strength index (RSI)
RSI momentum indicators'  wani tsinkene da ake amfani dashi a technical analysis wajen auna canjawar farashi na wata kadara tare da nuna irin yadda wannan kadara take acikin kasuwa kodai ansaya dayawa ko Kuma ansayar dayawa (overbought and oversold)
What does RSI telling you ? 
tsinke RSI Yana Kai kawo  tsakanin adadin lamba daga  0 zuwa 100 
A lisaffin tsinken Yana nuna idan yatafi qasa da 30 cewa ansayar da wannan kadara dayawa (oversold)  haka idan yatafi sama da 70 Yana nuna cewa ansayi wannan kadara dayawa Dole wani Abu yafaru kodai yadawo zuwa qasa reversal) ko Kuma yadawo Kamar zaiyi kasa sai Kuma ya yacigaba da tafiya (pullback ) 
RSI popular indicator ne Wanda J Weller' Wilder jr ya qirqireshi Kuma yagabatar dashi a shekara 1978
Interpretation of RSI and RSI ranges 
Hanya mafi sauki shine asakawa RSI horizontal lines guda biyu na sama a 70 percentage 
na qasa a 30 percentage Wanda idan yayi Cross 70% Yana nuna alamar bearish na reversal ko Kuma pullback  idan Kuma yayi Cross 30% Yana nuna alamar bullish
RSI bearish ranges RSI  zai kasance Akan 35% for a long time  but frequently saiya taba  70%  but Unable to break it ' is consider  reverse pattern hakan Yana nuna Mana the uptrend is weak mutum zai iya sell Amma ayi amfani da wasu alamomin domin tabbatar da hakan 
RSI Bullish ranges 
RSI zai kasance Akan 70% ko 65% for long time frequently sai yataba 35% but unable to break it ' is also consider as weak downtrend mutum zai iya buying but you have mix with another strategy to confirm the reversal 
Bullish  RSI divergence 
Bullish divergence ' RSI zai bayar da pattern na  oversold higher low Amma a price chart  zai bayar da lower low shima bullish signal ne
Bearish divergence RSI zai bayar da pattern na overbought lower high Amma price chart yabada Patten na higher high ' is bearish signal
Example of RSI swing rejection 
RSI zaiyi touching na 28% daga Nan zai haura kan 30% 
RSI zai tafi zuwa 40% daga Nan zai qara dawowa kan 30% again zai qara komawa yayi touching na 40% Wanda idan yayi breaking is bullish signal
Example of bearish RSI swing rejection 
RSI zaiyi touching na 82% daga Nan zai sauko zuwa qasa da 80% RSI zai tafi zuwa 70% zai qara komawa kan 80% daga Nan zai sauko zuwa 70%  zaiyi break-in wanda hakan yake nuna akwai bearish breakout
Conclusion 
RSI wani security ne dayake nuna maka damar Saya ko sayarwa 
Sannan RSI zai iya tafiya zuwa 80% ko 90% sannan zai iya tsayawa A 70% 75% na tsawon lokaci Wanda hakan yanada kyau muyi amfani da wasu dabarun domin kwasar riba 
Idan son samune ahada da wani strategy kamar Macd indicators ko ema yayi amfani da RSI 
Allah yabamu sa'a